{"name":"Helm Hardrasson","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"Aire","alignment":"CG","hitDice":"7","armorName":"hide armor","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"11 (16 with _barkskin_)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"45 (7d8 + 14)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"12","dexPoints":"10","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"12","wisPoints":"19","chaPoints":"13","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The druid can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The druid regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the druid can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the druid can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The druid can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the druid's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the druid's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the druid dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is a 7th-level spellcaster. His spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC [WIS SAVE], [WIS ATK] to hit with spell attacks). It has the following druid spells prepared:\n\n\n> * Cantrips (at will): _druidcraft, produce flame, shillelagh_\n> * 1st level (4 slots): _cure wounds, speak with animals, thunderwave_\n> * 2nd level (3 slots): _spike growth, darkvision, pass without a trace, lesser restoration_\n> * 3rd level (3 slots): _speak with plants, meld into stone, daylight_\n> * 4th level (1 slot): _hallucinatory terrain_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Wild Shape","desc":"[MON] polymorphs into a beast of CR 1/2 or lower (no fly speed).\nOptions: Crocodile, Black Bear, little critter."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"medicine","stat":"wis"},{"name":"nature","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Helm","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}